text: == Events == * Magnus Maximus returns to Britain to help them with the Barbarians raids. * An edict of Theodosius I closes pagan temples in the Nile Valley. * King Shapur III signs a treaty with Theodosius I. Armenia is divided in two kingdoms. * December 17 – Pope Siricius succeeds Damasus I as the 38th pope. == Births == * September 9 – Honorius, Roman Emperor * Chu Lingyuan, last empress of the Jin Dynasty * Maria, empress and daughter of Stilicho * Sengzhao, Chinese Buddhist * Wang Shen'ai, empress of the Jin Dynasty == Deaths == * December 11 – Pope Damasus I * Chu Suanzi, empress of the Jin Dynasty * Geungusu, king of Baekje * Murong Hong, founder of the Xianbei state Western Yan Category:380s
